Wind, People vs. Larry Flynt,

00:45:22.530 --> 00:45:26.020
Young Mr. Lincoln, Judgment
at Nuremburg, The Verdict.

00:45:26.020 --> 00:45:28.720
These true stories are
not necessarily popular

00:45:28.720 --> 00:45:32.820
because they're true, but because
they exemplify through 100 years

00:45:32.820 --> 00:45:37.190
of cinema the central ties
that bind film world making

00:45:37.190 --> 00:45:39.210
to legal world making.

00:45:39.210 --> 00:45:43.270 position:56%
