00:48:43.440 --> 00:48:47.480
we will distort or it will
be distorted or mismanaged

00:48:47.480 --> 00:48:49.190
through our expectations.

00:48:49.190 --> 00:48:52.810
Do people watch Judge Judy
or did they watch Judge Ito

00:48:52.810 --> 00:48:56.990
