think you're not altering the events

00:49:08.960 --> 00:49:10.530
that are being filmed?

00:49:10.530 --> 00:49:13.560
Are you not becoming the part
of the story that's being told?

00:49:13.560 --> 00:49:18.200
The thin blue line famously
