00:49:18.200 --> 00:49:20.020
for the defendant in that case.

00:49:20.020 --> 00:49:24.000
The paradox at the heart of Making
a Murderer is the same thing.

00:49:24.000 --> 00:49:26.780
The podcast sensation, the
serial, the same thing.

00:49:26.780 --> 00:49:30.040 position:56%
It's also at the heart of the debate
