considered, not just the film alone.

00:55:30.010 --> 00:55:32.190
So he does not fall
victim to the illusion

00:55:32.190 --> 00:55:34.520
of reality that the film portrays.

00:55:34.520 --> 00:55:37.760
He did not repeat the mistake
of that first film audience,

00:55:37.760 --> 00:55:44.220
