it has to be evaluated.

00:56:05.120 --> 00:56:07.710 position:56%
It must be cross-examined, actually,

00:56:07.710 --> 00:56:10.570
to understand what it really
means for the case at hand.

00:56:10.570 --> 00:56:12.070
So the history of law and film

00:56:12.070 --> 00:56:15.880
and television is really an
idealized story of heroes

00:56:15.880 --> 00:56:19.220
